{"type": "article", "id": 25713, "title": "宠物的小空间", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-21T06:40:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 61, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133424oTsPRxLcfyH9CBEm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">如果你虽然不希望自己的宠物爬上家具，但同时又想让它们拥有一个自己的空间，<a href=\"http://www.phiaro.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">Phiaro</a> 的设计师们为你想了一个办法：看似普通的茶几下暗藏玄机，让宠物可以在里面小憩，提升了空间的利用率。除此之外，他们还设计了一款穹顶风格的宠物小窝。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133422m6z5U3TuVCQkeRdn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133423ijvQ186rClJSI5FW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.35428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133423G6pHdYv7wEkOqic0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.35428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021334243TwQhDL9SckMZqpR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.35428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}